            <uuid>0330a7bd-d1c7-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
          <link name="link2" internal="false" type="A">
            <target><![CDATA[http://example/]]></target>
          </link>
        </links>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>If you have done the examples of chapter 1, you can skip this preparation step.</p>
<p>Otherwise, open the <a href="%(link0)">Launchpad</a> from the Quick launch menu, and in the launchpad select the <a href="%(link1)">Websites app</a>.</p>
<p>Use the wand icon to create a new website.</p>
<p>Type in the following data:</p>
<p><strong>Title</strong>: Examples<br /><strong>Server URL</strong>: <a href="%(link2)">http://example/</a><br /><strong>Encryption</strong>: No SSL encryption</p>
<p>This will create a new website in the <code>/sites/examples</code> folder. Leave the rest as is for now.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
